raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Hey Nina!
PlayerM: I was wondering if you're free for the weekend?
Nina: Who the hell is this?
PlayerM: Oh uhm... It's Mabel? We met in orientation?
PlayerM: Sorry if I'm bothering you
Nina: Wait I remember you LMAO
Nina: That cute little pink thing
PlayerM: That's me!
Nina: Whaddya want girlie pop
PlayerM: Oh uhm, I was wondering if you were doing anything tomorrow?
Nina: I was gonna go to the club tomorrow
Nina: Meet up with this dude who's been begging me for some time together
PlayerM: Oh is he like someone you're dating?
Nina: Pfft fuck no
PlayerM: Oh I see, I hope it goes well then
PlayerM: I guess you're busy
Nina: Hold up
Nina: I'm coming over to grab you tomorrow
Nina: But I seriously need to dig into your closet
Nina: I can't have you embarassing me like a chihuahua with a bowtie
PlayerM: Oh well, yeah! 
PlayerM: I'm okay with wearing anything
Nina: Perfect
Nina: I need to do some recruiting anyway or Jess is gonna yank my ear off
PlayerM: Recruiting? For what?
Nina: Nevermind your pretty little head about that girlie pop
Nina: I'll come by tomorrow... whenever I feel like it
PlayerM: That's a little hard to prepare for but sure thing!
PlayerM: Have a nice day!
Nina: Wth 😂
=> END"
